Package model

Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
model.GameObject
Direct Known Subclasses:
Boost, Brick, EndFlag, Enemy, Fireball, Mario
public abstract class GameObject extends Object
The main abstract class used to define lower-level game objects, like bricks and entities.
Version:
1.0.0
